參考聯合國人權宣言。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:27:13.000Z","msg":"非常中肯的回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cc58a74c28cf47a3fcc98431988865a5c784ae","tid":1256184,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:39:36.000Z","msg":"hk雞報同大公文匯同一水平"},{"pid":"1d1569a7eda91b18ef4b5b164aab6c23e4cd8059","tid":1256184,"uid":63808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:42:48.000Z","msg":"有之前致年青人條片的經驗，今次應該點應對？冷處理？拍多條片counter effect?"},{"pid":"f2a4ebb550ee7bce1172b7dddc3d5e545df2e0a1","tid":1256184,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又香港 G報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實點解會自稱雞報咁on9?</blockquote><br />\n問薑蓉"},{"pid":"d0386700eefa7a7287b0e2015baa67c46a4a8ad7","tid":1256184,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2a4ebb550ee7bce1172b7dddc3d5e545df2e0a1","tid":1256184,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又香港 G報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實點解會自稱雞報咁on9?</blockquote><br />\n問薑蓉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:03:29.000Z","msg":"扮高登出品昆細路仔睇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99767d4d6b452e26f0d3faa0172821aa2663ee6","tid":1256184,"uid":169027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"420e111124e62954ce765b83df83a28714e2c5cd","tid":1256184,"uid":44646,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"quote":{"pid":"b90ae531c9a1de21ff296e6922a584029ceecad3","tid":1256184,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:06:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkgpao.com/articles/1003338\" dat